1
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:12,080
Bowen,

2
00:00:13,190 --> 00:00:15,390
how long are you going to hide it from me?

3
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:17,090
What do you mean?

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,760
That day when Zhou Rong came to our house,

5
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,120
I saw everything from the stairs—

6
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,230
he was going to pull out a gun
to kill you.

7
00:00:24,230 --> 00:00:25,280
I almost rushed in

8
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,080
to fight them.

9
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:34,000
This is what they call "brothers are

10
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,660
the best partners in a fight."

11
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,940
My love for you wasn't in vain.

12
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,970
Our parents passed away early.

13
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:43,350
You raised me alone.

14
00:00:44,030 --> 00:00:45,790
You earned our family's success today

15
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:46,640
by risking your life

16
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:47,670
and fighting for it

17
00:00:47,670 --> 00:00:49,000
through thick and thin.

18
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:50,520
I know you don't want me

19
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,410
to be like you.

20
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,290
You want me to succeed in my studies.

21
00:00:53,290 --> 00:00:54,120
All my efforts

22
00:00:54,150 --> 00:00:55,470
are for this goal.

23
00:00:58,350 --> 00:00:59,880
And my painstaking efforts

24
00:01:00,670 --> 00:01:01,930
haven't gone to waste.

25
00:01:02,380 --> 00:01:02,980
Yangyang,

26
00:01:03,470 --> 00:01:05,000
when you finish your studies,

27
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,560
all the wealth I've built

28
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,360
will be yours.

29
00:01:07,710 --> 00:01:08,990
By then, you'll have both a diploma

30
00:01:08,990 --> 00:01:09,700
and wealth.

31
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,310
Flocks of girls

32
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:12,430
will be chasing after you.

33
00:01:12,430 --> 00:01:14,160
Bowen, I don't need any of that.

34
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,160
But I can't live without you.

35
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,510
You are the only family

36
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:19,640
I have in this world.

37
00:01:24,510 --> 00:01:25,640
Mr. Rong came to meet you that day

38
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,810
because the police were investigating

39
00:01:26,810 --> 00:01:28,140
Lu Zheng's case, right?

40
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,510
On his birthday,

41
00:01:29,510 --> 00:01:30,590
I heard everything

42
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,400
you guys said

43
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,350
in the wine cellar.

44
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:34,070
I'm afraid... I'm afraid
the police will trace it to you,

45
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:34,509
Bowen!

46
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,570
Don't worry.

47
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:37,150
There is nothing in Sanjiangkou

48
00:01:37,150 --> 00:01:38,590
that I, your brother, can't handle.

49
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:39,560
Your mission right now

50
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,560
is to focus on applying for college.

51
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,710
And then,

52
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,310
go abroad

53
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,060
and find someone with a high IQ

54
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:47,789
to improve

55
00:01:47,789 --> 00:01:49,350
our Lang family's genes.

56
00:01:49,789 --> 00:01:51,450
Someone with a low IQ won't do.

57
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:19,610
[Born with Luck]

58
00:03:19,650 --> 00:03:22,570
[Episode 12]

59
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,190
Ren!

60
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:28,750
What's up so early?

61
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:31,550
You're looking for Yibo?

62
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,400
He's not with me.

63
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:37,480
Okay.

64
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,329
Hu Jianren is already downstairs.

65
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,000
Zhou Rong wanted to see me

66
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,930
and sent him to pick me up in person.

67
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:04,870
Can we get through this?

68
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:31,530
Take it.

69
00:04:32,310 --> 00:04:33,110
Don't hang up.

70
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:34,600
If I say,

71
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,000
"I don't know anything about it.

72
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,130
Please go ask Yibo,"

73
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,409
call the police immediately.

74
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:42,580
I know Zhou Rong so well.

75
00:04:43,050 --> 00:04:44,390
This is way too risky.

76
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:46,090
Is there any other way?

77
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:50,510
If he dares to do anything to you,

78
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:52,310
I'll fight him to the bitter end.

79
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,020
I'm coming.

80
00:05:06,820 --> 00:05:08,820
Ren, sorry to have kept you waiting.

81
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:50,020
[Waiting]

82
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:49,470
[Jiafu Digital Store]

83
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,410
Come in.

84
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,040
Welcome.

85
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,430
Mr. Rong.

86
00:07:25,970 --> 00:07:27,510
Let me introduce a new friend to you.

87
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:27,970
Come on.

88
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:30,600
Sit down.

89
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,870
Mr. Rong told you to sit down.

90
00:07:33,870 --> 00:07:34,240
I...

91
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:36,530
Don't be afraid. Just sit down.

92
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,040
Sit.

93
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,250
Take your seat.

94
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:46,800
Don't be afraid.

95
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,750
As long as you tell the truth,

96
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,210
there won't be any danger.

97
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:54,920
I promise I will tell the truth.

98
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,760
I heard

99
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:57,950
that the police
went to ask you about it again.

100
00:07:57,950 --> 00:07:58,630
Recall carefully

101
00:07:58,630 --> 00:07:59,560
what they asked.

102
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,520
Don't leave out any details.

103
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:04,750
I... I...

104
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,560
Based on the latest information

105
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,430
we have,

106
00:08:17,870 --> 00:08:19,190
Captain Ye did go to Fenglinwan

107
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,390
before the accident.

108
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,310
We asked Lu Yibo.

109
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,090
He said that

110
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,960
when Captain Ye went to meet him,

111
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,890
he also asked about this watch.

112
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:28,920
So,

113
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,390
Captain Ye also noticed

114
00:08:31,390 --> 00:08:33,030
something fishy about this watch.

115
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,950
[Checked the cases handled by Lu Zheng]
[Drunk driving inspection] [Murdered]

116
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:36,990
Could it be related to Chief Lu's death?

117
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,429
It can't be verified yet.

118
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,560
[Waiting] [Speaker]

119
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,160
I explained the jewelry thing clearly.

120
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,480
But they kept asking

121
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:54,180
if Captain Ye had been to Fenglinwan

122
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,830
before the accident.

123
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,800
What did you say then?

124
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,360
I didn't know

125
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,570
what they wanted.

126
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,910
So when I was at the police station,

127
00:09:02,910 --> 00:09:04,510
I didn't say he had been here.

128
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:06,000
I said I didn't know.

129
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:10,780
That's all?

130
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,360
Think again.

131
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:16,800
The watch.

132
00:09:17,820 --> 00:09:18,800
About the watch.

133
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:20,720
What watch?

134
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,390
They a-asked about the watch

135
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,720
that Bowen gave to Yibo.

136
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,440
But this watch was

137
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,790
not purchased by Lu Yibo himself.

138
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,550
It was Lang Bowen

139
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:31,270
[Zhou Rong] [Hu Jianren] [Lang Bowen]

140
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,670
who lost it to him when they were

141
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:31,530
playing a game.

142
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,960
Then it might be

143
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,260
related to Lang Bowen.

144
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,320
Captain Wang and I

145
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,650
deduced the same thing.

146
00:09:37,210 --> 00:09:37,840
However,

147
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,110
Lu Yibo told us

148
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:41,390
that Lang Bowen lost this watch

149
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,360
[Zhou Rong] [Hu Jianren] [Lang Bowen]

150
00:09:41,410 --> 00:09:42,480
to him a year ago.

151
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:44,390
A year ago,

152
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,720
Chief Lu was still alive.

153
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:47,460
Yeah.

154
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,200
So now all of this

155
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,720
is pointing to Lu Yibo again.

156
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:52,750
[General Manager of Fenglinwan Hotel]

157
00:09:52,770 --> 00:09:53,360
[PR Manager of Fenglinwan Nightclub]

158
00:09:53,470 --> 00:09:54,120
It's so important,

159
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,360
and you are only telling me now?

160
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,000
Mr. Rong.

161
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,030
Mr. Rong.

162
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,840
Yibo is actually

163
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:00,140
very loyal to you.

164
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,320
If he's so loyal,

165
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,980
why didn't he tell us earlier?

166
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:05,720
I don't know anything.

167
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,280
Please go ask Yibo.

168
00:10:08,310 --> 00:10:10,650
[Chief Zhang Yi'ang
of the Municipal Bureau]

169
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:14,600
It's Lu Yibo.

170
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:17,030
Hello?

171
00:10:17,170 --> 00:10:17,900
Chief Zhang,

172
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:19,820
this is Lu Yibo speaking.

173
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,650
I want to confess to you.

174
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,440
Good.

175
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,240
What do you want to confess?

176
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:24,600
Go ahead.

177
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,530
I confess to you.

178
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,400
I'll tell you.

179
00:10:26,570 --> 00:10:28,230
Confess what? I'm listening.

180
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,440
I'll tell you everything.

181
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,280
I know.

182
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,860
Take your time.

183
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,740
The night Lu Zheng died,

184
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:38,600
Bowen was wearing that watch.

185
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,110
Later, he gave it to Yibo.

186
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,660
Yibo was afraid of being implicated,

187
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,790
so he asked me to throw the watch away.

188
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,190
I didn't dare to tell you.

189
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:50,600
Mr. Rong,

190
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,300
I'll go bring Lu Yibo here.

191
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,360
If you can't do it,

192
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:54,030
I will.

193
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,320
Mr. Rong!

194
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,420
You can't do this to Yibo.

195
00:10:57,630 --> 00:10:58,910
Yibo already confessed

196
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,750
that before Lu Zheng died,

197
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:02,880
Bowen had already given him the watch.

198
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,800
What do you mean?

199
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,320
Y-Yibo knew he had let you down before,

200
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,320
Mr. Rong,

201
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,480
so he took it all on himself.

202
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,960
The police won't be able
to trace it to Bowen

203
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,440
or to you.

204
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,670
Even if they trace it to you,

205
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,540
he has already taken the fall for you.

206
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:31,630
Verify this matter

207
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:32,670
with that bastard.

208
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:33,120
Yes.

209
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:36,080
Hello?

210
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,780
[Chief Zhang Yi'ang
of the Municipal Bureau]

211
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:38,630
Hello?

212
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,130
What's this all about?

213
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,960
Is he playing with us?

214
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:51,060
[Chief Zhang Yi'ang
of the Municipal Bureau]

215
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:25,840
Ren.

216
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:34,790
What are you doing here?

217
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,200
I...

218
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,840
I've always wanted to learn photography.

219
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,240
So I came to buy some gear.

220
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:46,120
I have a question for you.

221
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,050
Please go ahead.

222
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:50,400
Who is it?

223
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,240
Nobody.

224
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,620
Take it out.

225
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,200
Really, it's nobody.

226
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:12,160
[Chief Zhang Yi'ang
of the Municipal Bureau]

227
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,650
I don't know why

228
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,900
he's calling me.

229
00:13:16,230 --> 00:13:17,600
You tailed us here.

230
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:20,840
Ren,

231
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:22,720
it's not what you think.

232
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,170
It really isn't.

233
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:27,510
Mr. Lu,

234
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:28,770
what do you

235
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:29,690
mean by this?

236
00:13:31,510 --> 00:13:32,030
Ren,

237
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,990
please don't talk like that.

238
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,040
You can either hit me or scold me.

239
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:37,240
You being this polite

240
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,120
scares me.

241
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,390
Mr. Lu.

242
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:41,630
Mr. Lu.

243
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,720
Ren, Ren.

244
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:45,240
You...

245
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:47,000
You can interrogate me inside.

246
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,240
Let's go inside to talk.

247
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,360
If you think I'm lying,

248
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,000
you can kill me inside,

249
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,360
and no one will see it, right?

250
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:51,980
Let's go inside and talk.

251
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:52,480
Ren,

252
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:53,720
let's g-go inside.

253
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:54,420
Come on.

254
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,440
After you.

255
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,520
Stay outside.

256
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,720
Qi came over today,

257
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,550
and you knew
what Mr. Rong wanted to ask her,

258
00:14:12,550 --> 00:14:13,680
so you followed her.

259
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,360
If anything happened to Qi,

260
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,620
you'd call the police,

261
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,390
right?

262
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,630
Mr. Rong hates people

263
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:25,430
who are disloyal to him the most.

264
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:29,000
Ren.

265
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,200
As long as you don't tell Mr. Rong,

266
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,600
I'll do anything you ask.

267
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,920
I'm afraid of Mr. Rong, too.

268
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,710
I don't dare to hide it from him.

269
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,000
Ren,

270
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:54,400
[Security Office Management System]

271
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,870
the God of Wealth statue
you got for Mr. Rong

272
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,330
wasn't that price, right?

273
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,120
Zheng Yongbing is

274
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,520
a regular at Fenglinwan.

275
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:00,960
These past couple of years,

276
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:03,510
you've handled everything big or small
in Rongcheng.

277
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:05,440
You must've raked in a lot of money.

278
00:15:08,460 --> 00:15:09,670
Mr. Rong hates people

279
00:15:09,670 --> 00:15:11,470
who are disloyal to him the most.

280
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:19,120
Are you threatening me?

281
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,480
How would I have that audacity?

282
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,150
Ren,

283
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,720
the police already know about this.

284
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:27,480
Really?

285
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,670
T-There's another thing

286
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:31,730
I haven't dared to report to Mr. Rong.

287
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:33,740
Out with it!

288
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,630
On the night Ye Jian died,

289
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:40,900
